# A list contains problems of linux I encountered

Cisco anyConnect
Need to update the repository:
sudo add-apt-repository deb http://gb.archive.ubuntu.com/ubuntu jammy main
sudo apt update
sudo apt install libwebkit2gtk-4.0-dev


Torrent
1. Stop the torrent
2. Create new destination
3. Move the torrent folders/files
4. Set the location to new location in the torrent client
5. Force recheck
6. Check the torrent as it should display a running progress bar
7. Star the torrent

# The setting location might be tricky so try selecting different folder setup till the bar is green
# Double check the folder path so you will not get headache